snippet.title: Westwood Shadows Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Heavily influenced by the legacy of legendary survival horror game series like Resident Evil and Silent Hill, Westwood Shadows invites you to a dark adventure, where conspiracy, fear and mystery offer a terrifying experience.

Add the game to your wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1122360/Westwood_Shadows/

Play the Prologue on Steam for free: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1717810/Westwood_Shadows_Prologue/

#survivalhorror #horror #stealth #gameplaytrailer #game #fear
